<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>中国新闻|今日突发新闻 |路透社</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/</link><description>Reuters.com 是您获取最新中国新闻故事和时事的在线来源，确保我们的读者及时了解任何突发新闻动态 - 由 RSSHub 提供支持</description><lastBuildDate>Thu, 25 Jul 2024 06:18:35 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>阿斯利康因治疗需求乐观而上调全年展望</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/healthcare-pharmaceuticals/astrazeneca-lifts-full-year-outlook-upbeat-demand-therapies-2024-07-25/</link><description>英瑞制药商阿斯利康 (AstraZeneca) 周四上调了 2024 年的销售额和利润预测，并超出了分析师对其第二季度营收的预期，原因是对其癌症和罕见疾病疗法的需求提振。</description><pubDate>Thu, 25 Jul 2024 06:07:41 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/healthcare-pharmaceuticals/astrazeneca-lifts-full-year-outlook-upbeat-demand-therapies-2024-07-25/</guid></item><item><title>Stellantis 上半年收入和营业收入下降，未达到预期</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/stellantis-misses-forecasts-with-h1-drop-revenue-operating-income-2024-07-25/</link><description>由于充满挑战的行业环境和内部运营问题（尤其是在北美），Stellantis 上半年的收入和营业利润下降幅度超过预期，导致该汽车制造商在此期间烧钱。</description><pubDate>Thu, 25 Jul 2024 05:39:15 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/stellantis-misses-forecasts-with-h1-drop-revenue-operating-income-2024-07-25/</guid></item><item><title>联合利华出售 Truliva 股份</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/deals/unilever-sells-stake-truliva-2024-07-25/</link><description>联合利华周四表示，已出售其在沁源集团（又名 Truliva）的股份，但未透露出售的财务条款。</description><pubDate>Thu, 25 Jul 2024 05:26:54 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/deals/unilever-sells-stake-truliva-2024-07-25/</guid></item><item><title>人工智能的繁荣帮助 Besi 抵消了第二季度中国主流市场的疲软</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/technology/chipmaking-parts-supplier-besi-posts-better-than-expected-q2-orders-2024-07-25/</link><description>荷兰芯片制造零部件供应商BE半导体工业公司（Besi）周四第二季度新订单超出预期，因为对其用于人工智能和其他先进封装应用的系统的需求部分抵消了主流组装市场和中国增长疲弱的影响。</description><pubDate>Thu, 25 Jul 2024 04:56:38 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/technology/chipmaking-parts-supplier-besi-posts-better-than-expected-q2-orders-2024-07-25/</guid></item><item><title>市场分析师对中国意外降息的反应</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/market-analysts-react-surprise-rate-cut-china-2024-07-25/</link><description>中国周四非周期削减银行融资成本，令金融市场感到意外。在宣布将一年期中期贷款便利 (MLF) 下调 20 个基点后，股市下跌，债券上涨。</description><pubDate>Thu, 25 Jul 2024 04:34:53 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/market-analysts-react-surprise-rate-cut-china-2024-07-25/</guid></item><item><title>中国央行再次以较低利率放贷，令人意外</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/china-central-bank-surprises-by-lending-again-lower-rates-2024-07-25/</link><description>中国央行周四以极低的利率进行了计划外贷款操作，本周第二次令市场感到意外，这表明当局正试图提供更大规模的货币刺激措施以支撑经济。</description><pubDate>Thu, 25 Jul 2024 04:01:02 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/china-central-bank-surprises-by-lending-again-lower-rates-2024-07-25/</guid></item><item><title>台风期间货轮在台湾海域沉没 九名船员失踪</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/freighter-sinks-off-taiwan-during-typhoon-nine-crew-missing-2024-07-25/</link><description>台湾消防部门周四表示，一艘悬挂坦桑尼亚国旗、载有九名缅甸公民的货轮在台风期间在南部港口城市高雄海岸沉没，船员尚未做出回应。</description><pubDate>Thu, 25 Jul 2024 03:28:22 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/freighter-sinks-off-taiwan-during-typhoon-nine-crew-missing-2024-07-25/</guid></item><item><title>BASIC集团猛烈抨击气候变化和金融领域的“领导力无效”</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/environment/basic-bloc-slams-leadership-void-climate-change-finance-2024-07-25/</link><description>巴西、南非、印度和中国组成的基础四国集团周三晚间表示，富裕国家在气候政治方面留下了“领导力真空”，必须提供数万亿美元来帮助发展中国家减少温室气体排放。</description><pubDate>Thu, 25 Jul 2024 03:16:16 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/environment/basic-bloc-slams-leadership-void-climate-change-finance-2024-07-25/</guid></item><item><title>香港法院驳回大亨黎智英终止审判的请求</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/hong-kong-court-dismisses-bid-end-jimmy-lai-trial-2024-07-25/</link><description>香港一家法院周四驳回了法律团队对被监禁的民主党人黎智英结束国家安全审判的请求，称检察官似乎有足够的证据支持对他的所有三项指控。</description><pubDate>Thu, 25 Jul 2024 02:52:51 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/hong-kong-court-dismisses-bid-end-jimmy-lai-trial-2024-07-25/</guid></item><item><title>科技股暴跌打击亚洲股市，日元升至 2-1/2 个月高点</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/global-markets-wrapup-1-2024-07-25/</link><description>由于全球科技股暴跌，投资者纷纷转向风险较低的资产，包括短期债券、日元和瑞士法郎，亚洲股市周四遭受重创。</description><pubDate>Thu, 25 Jul 2024 02:36:59 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/global-markets-wrapup-1-2024-07-25/</guid></item><item><title>油价因中国需求疲软和中东停火谈判而下跌</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/energy/oil-prices-ease-concerns-over-weak-china-demand-mideast-ceasefire-talks-2024-07-25/</link><description>由于对全球最大原油进口国中国需求疲软的担忧以及对中东即将达成停火协议的预期克服了美国库存减少后前一交易日的涨幅，油价周四下跌。</description><pubDate>Thu, 25 Jul 2024 01:35:41 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/energy/oil-prices-ease-concerns-over-weak-china-demand-mideast-ceasefire-talks-2024-07-25/</guid></item><item><title>套利交易平仓、风险情绪恶化，日元大幅上涨</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/currencies/yen-rises-carry-trades-unwind-risk-sentiment-takes-hit-2024-07-25/</link><description>由于日元套利交易平仓和风险偏好恶化，周四日元兑美元汇率升至 2-1/2 个月来的最高水平，并在下周日本央行 (BOJ) 会议之前兑其他货币升至数月高点。</description><pubDate>Thu, 25 Jul 2024 01:05:16 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/currencies/yen-rises-carry-trades-unwind-risk-sentiment-takes-hit-2024-07-25/</guid></item><item><title>台风“盖美”在台湾海域击沉货轮，冲向中国沿海</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/typhoon-gaemi-passes-over-taiwan-heads-chinese-coast-2024-07-25/</link><description>周四，台风“嘉美”横扫台湾北部，造成两人死亡，引发洪水并沉没一艘货轮，然后向西穿过台湾海峡，抵达中国大陆，预计将带来更多暴雨。</description><pubDate>Thu, 25 Jul 2024 00:29:55 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/typhoon-gaemi-passes-over-taiwan-heads-chinese-coast-2024-07-25/</guid></item><item><title>中资银行下调存款利率以缓解利润率挤压</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/major-chinese-banks-cut-deposit-rates-after-reduction-lending-rates-2024-07-25/</link><description>中国五家主要国有银行周四下调了存款利率，以缓解本周意外降低贷款基准以提振经济增长后对本已创纪录低位利润率的打击。</description><pubDate>Thu, 25 Jul 2024 00:07:08 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/major-chinese-banks-cut-deposit-rates-after-reduction-lending-rates-2024-07-25/</guid></item><item><title>专家称，中国的秘密航天飞机可能正在测试“双重用途”技术</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/technology/space/chinas-secretive-spaceplane-likely-testing-dual-use-technology-experts-say-2024-07-25/</link><description>专家表示，中国的无人可重复使用航天器在火箭助推器顶部发射，降落在一个秘密军用机场，很可能是在测试技术，但也可用于操纵或回收卫星。</description><pubDate>Thu, 25 Jul 2024 00:04:49 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/technology/space/chinas-secretive-spaceplane-likely-testing-dual-use-technology-experts-say-2024-07-25/</guid></item></channel></rss>